warehouse

Interface IWarehouseObservable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IObservable<IProduct>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Warehouse

    public interface IWarehouseObservable
extends IObservable<IProduct>
    Specific interface for a Warehouse observer. It sets the generic type of the IObservable interface to IProduct. This interface does not redefine any methods and is only introduced to make handling of observers easier.

    OOP
